snippet.title: Old School Rally - Official Fall 2024 Update Trailer
snippet.description:
The long-awaited Fall major update for Old School Rally is finally here!

Split-Screen Mode, New Stages, New Cars, and More!

Old School Rally is now available on Steam Early Access.
Get it here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2824660/Old_School_Rally/
